---
import Landing from '@/layout/Landing.astro';
---

<Landing 
    title="Legal Notice" 
    description="Legal information about Anyclazz S.L. and the terms governing the use of our platform."
    keywords={['legal notice', 'terms', 'regulations', 'compliance']}
>
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-20 max-w-4xl">
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-[var(--color-neutral-900)]">Legal Notice</h1>
            <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-neutral-600)] mb-8">Revised Version</p>

            <section class="mb-10">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-[var(--color-neutral-800)]">1. General Information</h2>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)] mb-4">
                    In compliance with applicable regulations, including Law 34/2002 of July 11 on Information Society
                    Services and Electronic Commerce (LSSI-CE), the following information is provided:
                </p>
                <ul class="list-none space-y-2 text-[var(--color-neutral-700)]">
                    <li><strong>Company name:</strong> Anyclazz S.L.</li>
                    <li><strong>Tax ID / Registration number:</strong> B-22956890</li>
                    <li><strong>Registered address:</strong> Calle Calvo Sotelo, 7, Piso 2, Puerta B, 28660 – Boadilla del Monte (Madrid), Spain</li>
                    <li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:info@anyclazz.com" class="text-[var(--color-primary-600)] hover:underline">info@anyclazz.com</a></li>
                </ul>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)] mt-4">
                    Anyclazz S.L. is the owner of the platform and website (hereinafter, the "Platform").
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-10">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-[var(--color-neutral-800)]">2. Purpose</h2>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)] mb-4">
                    This Legal Notice regulates access to and use of the Platform.
                </p>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)]">
                    Accessing and using the Platform implies full acceptance of the terms set out herein.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-10">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-[var(--color-neutral-800)]">3. Conditions of Use</h2>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)] mb-4">Users agree to use the Platform in accordance with:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-[var(--color-neutral-700)] ml-4">
                    <li>Applicable law (including US laws where relevant)</li>
                    <li>Good faith</li>
                    <li>Public order</li>
                </ul>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)] mt-4 mb-2">Users shall refrain from:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-[var(--color-neutral-700)] ml-4">
                    <li>Engaging in unlawful or fraudulent activities</li>
                    <li>Causing damage to the Platform or its systems</li>
                    <li>Attempting unauthorized access to data or accounts</li>
                </ul>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)] mt-4">
                    Anyclazz reserves the right to deny or withdraw access to users who violate these conditions.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-10">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-[var(--color-neutral-800)]">4. Intellectual and Industrial Property</h2>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)] mb-4">
                    All contents of the Platform are protected by intellectual property laws.
                </p>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)]">
                    Reproduction or distribution without authorization is prohibited.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-10">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-[var(--color-neutral-800)]">5. Liability</h2>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)] mb-4">
                    Anyclazz is not responsible for misuse, user content, technical errors, or damages from use.
                </p>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)]">
                    No guarantee of continuous availability or absence of errors.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-10">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-[var(--color-neutral-800)]">6. External Links</h2>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)]">
                    Anyclazz is not responsible for third-party websites.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-10">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-[var(--color-neutral-800)]">7. Data Protection</h2>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)]">
                    See <a href="/legal/privacy-policy" class="text-[var(--color-primary-600)] hover:underline">Privacy Policy</a>.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-10">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-[var(--color-neutral-800)]">8. Cookies</h2>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)]">
                    See <a href="/legal/cookie-policy" class="text-[var(--color-primary-600)] hover:underline">Cookie Policy</a>.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-10">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-[var(--color-neutral-800)]">9. Applicable Law and Dispute Resolution</h2>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)] mb-4">
                    Spanish law applies to EEA users.
                </p>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)] mb-4">
                    US users: disputes resolved via arbitration (AAA or JAMS).
                </p>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)]">
                    Small claims court rights remain.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-10">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-[var(--color-neutral-800)]">10. Contact</h2>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)]">
                    <a href="mailto:info@anyclazz.com" class="text-[var(--color-primary-600)] hover:underline">info@anyclazz.com</a>
                </p>
            </section>
        </div>
    </div>
</Landing>
